Check out our 2022 Omni, Carbon Omni & Future Omni skis! Available now!

The Omni was designed with a Hybrid Waist Width, halfway between those typically found in traditional skis and those in wideride skis. This provides for smooth instinctive turns at a wide range of speeds. 

For 2022 the Omni & Carbon Omni are also offered in a Wide Edition in the 67 & 69" lengths, providing additional lift for easier getups and stable turns. Find out why the Omni ski shape quickly became a best seller.

For more features of the Omni & Carbon Omni, go to hosports.com!

latestPosts.caption:
🏆 JAIMEE BULL TAKES THE WIN… AGAIN! 🏆⁠
⁠
Jaimee claimed the Botaski Pro title in spectacular style, battling her way through a gnarly 39off/10.75m pass to lay down the gauntlet 💥⁠
⁠
Allie came heartbreakingly close, charging all the way to just inside 6 at 39, but it wasn’t quite enough to take down Jaimee this time!⁠
⁠
Another win on the board. Another masterclass from the champ.⁠
⁠
📸 - robhazelwoodcreative

Allie storms her way into the Final at the Botaski Pro! 💥⁠
Sitting just behind Jaimee in 2nd, she’s looking locked in and ready for the head-to-head finals tomorrow 🔥⁠
⁠
On the Men’s side, every Syndicate skier punched their ticket to the Final which means we've got 4 out of the 8 spots locked down!⁠
⁠
With head-to-heads, anything can happen so we’re all in to see how it shakes out tomorrow 👀⚔️
